{"title":"悼秦基伟同志","authors":["罗应怀"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":3,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼秦基伟同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗应怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊悉基伟子夜逝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老泪斑斑肝肠断。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄麻群起擎义旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西行转进战陕川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历险祁连英雄勇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威震太行寇胆寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逐鹿江淮才华展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰骋边陲扫匪叛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请缨入朝情如铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上甘岭役慑敌胆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华北演习凭运筹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国庆阅兵费操办。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治军安邦身先卒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国泰民强力如磐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战将功勋垂千古，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高风亮节照人寰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９９７年２月１２日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}